title: MU softball game is postponed
maintext:
HUNTINGTON — Marshall University’s softball game Tuesday against Morehead State at Dot Hicks Field is postponed.
The teams will play an April 11 doubleheader beginning at 1 p.m.
Marshall is at home Saturday and Sunday for a doubleheader with Southern Miss. Saturday’s doubleheader begins at 1 p.m. Sunday is a noon game.
